aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1d7aad4bf17ef94097f58420ebbd79a80b9fb9","tid":1123261,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"但個盾係邊度黎先 ca做既野已經產生時間悖倫"},{"pid":"323ea5d8414e5bf12c5e6a5db04c4699fda8a224","tid":1123261,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1d7aad4bf17ef94097f58420ebbd79a80b9fb9","tid":1123261,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"但個盾係邊度黎先 ca做既野已經產生時間悖倫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:04:18.000Z","msg":"個盾咪Tony 老豆比佢囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b1fc9450244ef14f24b1a2b66d396a0bbefe4b","tid":1123261,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"柒得過全女班果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b028e4d0be58cd5bdbf20ec110645ea6b1f67e49","tid":1123261,"uid":199352,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"係咪得我好鍾意Falcon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782a8a854d9f00e69910c1155bcc46d2f4ec7b78","tid":1123261,"uid":104883,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:56:45.000Z","msg":"說好的 till the end of the line 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9086dfab53f863880d976136856c3c272f61cce3","tid":1123261,"uid":207005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"088f937a50c3c3d5e0aae9d82d7202ab246e1785","tid":1123261,"uid":70448,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"mcu bucky好與世無爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢應該唔肯做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T23:05:26.000Z","msg":"佢要著白豹裝甲又點做美隊呀"},{"pid":"ce0b048f159e5b380e3ab2417484a75600ee542b","tid":1123261,"uid":18060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"983d035b3758a77c767867c0ecded024f687fe1a","tid":1123261,"uid":60588,"like":121,"dislike":2,"score":119,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得成班女個幕重難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T23:32:16.000Z","msg":"真 又係over左"},{"pid":"deddd2bbf07ca51a7885df9a6c8465a3bec0f232","tid":1123261,"uid":232687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T23:53:24.000Z","msg":"講實力,領袖風範,個人魅力<br />\nFalcon呢個角色根本就carry唔起CA呢個身份"},{"pid":"cf2287291a16dbcbb3ecc1315df625730243d4a1","tid":1123261,"uid":203743,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"第一，Falcon同Bucky係漫畫都做過CA，唔存在漫畫衝突。<br />\n<br />\n第二，CA係軍隊/國家形象大使，理應傳個盾俾價值觀相似嘅繼承人。最直觀嘅繼承人就係跟左CA幾套戲嘅Falcon。<br />\n<br />\n第三，Bucky同Steve本身各有各打。Steve未變身之前，Bucky已經衝鋒陷陣緊。同期，係Steve被選上做隊長，Bucky連諗都冇諗過。之後Steve上戰場，都只係同Bucky拍檔咗一陣，之後Bucky好快就假死。<br />\n<br />\n第四，Bucky個記錄太花。佢最大嘅超能力事蹟就係被Hydra改造，殺人如麻。而再之前佢只係一屆普通士兵，冇咩值得被人另眼相看嘅性格特徵。<br />\n<br />\nSteve已經用咗CA3成套戲做自私精，維護佢老友。而家佢老友連法律審訊都未接受，憑咩傳個盾俾佢？<br />\n佢傳盾俾Falcon起碼做咗一件公正嘅事。"},{"pid":"34d3fd4e0a64aad3028f1d8928223a9479a926ef","tid":1123261,"uid":35756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"Falcon係正統軍人<br />\nBucky係俾人洗咗腦嘅罪犯仲走埋佬去wakanda<br />\n<br />\n基本上得一個choice啫"},{"pid":"c8f22e115dfa91d0c329961d0798d3a9fbcb0f3e","tid":1123261,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:19:24.000Z","msg":"反而覺得個演員本身唔夠魅力，加上幾集以來其實無咩發揮"},{"pid":"4cc1f643f0523e45a7b3735752a11649c4cc0808","tid":1123261,"uid":203743,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cf2287291a16dbcbb3ecc1315df625730243d4a1","tid":1123261,"uid":203743,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"第一，Falcon同Bucky係漫畫都做過CA，唔存在漫畫衝突。<br />\n<br />\n第二，CA係軍隊/國家形象大使，理應傳個盾俾價值觀相似嘅繼承人。最直觀嘅繼承人就係跟左CA幾套戲嘅Falcon。<br />\n<br />\n第三，Bucky同Steve本身各有各打。Steve未變身之前，Bucky已經衝鋒陷陣緊。同期，係Steve被選上做隊長，Bucky連諗都冇諗過。之後Steve上戰場，都只係同Bucky拍檔咗一陣，之後Bucky好快就假死。<br />\n<br />\n第四，Bucky個記錄太花。佢最大嘅超能力事蹟就係被Hydra改造，殺人如麻。而再之前佢只係一屆普通士兵，冇咩值得被人另眼相看嘅性格特徵。<br />\n<br />\nSteve已經用咗CA3成套戲做自私精，維護佢老友。而家佢老友連法律審訊都未接受，憑咩傳個盾俾佢？<br />\n佢傳盾俾Falcon起碼做咗一件公正嘅事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:23:30.000Z","msg":"Falcon做緊班之前已經做緊超能力特種部隊成員。佢對美國嘅功蹟一定多過一介步兵Bucky。<br />\n個盾唔係Steve佢自己㗎。個盾係Howard Stark同博士寄託俾Steve嘅希望同社會責任。<br />\n係紀錄部隊入面，人人都需要做領袖，上面唔喺度，就下一級接手。Falcon冇展現領袖風範因為佢一直做緊Steve條𡃁。但係，以佢同Steve嘅對話，加上佢本人講嘢態度，佢絕對有領袖潛質。"},{"pid":"b57f462f4aabe55afece9269faaee5754e5db6d7","tid":1123261,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f398a482a3fb10f1ff66b4743fd46cf993003df7","tid":1123261,"uid":33527,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"我以為你想講堆女無啦啦集結送手套<br />\n我就真係覺得俾個幕搞臭成套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:58:49.000Z","msg":"呢個真，都唔知集嚟做乜，個場咁混亂都集合到，真係好突兀"},{"pid":"9ab2c0f105aa52c0d8094d48ffa965984548f92d","tid":1123261,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57f462f4aabe55afece9269faaee5754e5db6d7","tid":1123261,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f398a482a3fb10f1ff66b4743fd46cf993003df7","tid":1123261,"uid":33527,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"我以為你想講堆女無啦啦集結送手套<br />\n我就真係覺得俾個幕搞臭成套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:58:49.000Z","msg":"呢個真，都唔知集嚟做乜，個場咁混亂都集合到，真係好突兀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T00:59:56.000Z","msg":"呢場好核突，除左女權撚會好開心之外"},{"pid":"bd8de9912aa536c9150efcf1aa28d3917ec532ab","tid":1123261,"uid":4237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deddd2bbf07ca51a7885df9a6c8465a3bec0f232","tid":1123261,"uid":232687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T23:53:24.000Z","msg":"講實力,領袖風範,個人魅力<br />\nFalcon呢個角色根本就carry唔起CA呢個身份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"所以就係之後要睇佢成長"},{"pid":"a717ce61ee91440cacf98d99ab9234a552762f3c","tid":1123261,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:08:12.000Z","msg":"事實上漫畫sam的確係其中一位美國隊長"},{"pid":"537aeffb461daa5e5de5f4149d42c2002de0dd4d","tid":1123261,"uid":89155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:14:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得係少左個位去舖排。<br />\n漫畫入面falcon做到嘅唔只係跟班<br />\n而係一個有領導才能嘅角色<br />\n呢個都係我個人認為falcon較bucky適合做captain america, 因為captain america嘅角色係要領導avengers. bucky可能同steve rogers個人交情較好，能力都可能較好，但領導才能falcon係高好多。<br />\n所以漫畫入面steve rogers老左交比falcon做個位係冇咁突兀。<br />\n相反，電影入面塑造唔到falcon成為一個咁嘅角色，一路只係一個二打六。如果中間可以加插一幕佢捨身去救steve rogers之類，之後再比佢做美國隊長，成件事會smooth好多"},{"pid":"610fcd87cb150862cfabbfea2b1b7c37250c720f","tid":1123261,"uid":26106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5bd0556b01f09ccb83909445d586ae3eea9c6ec3","tid":1123261,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點撚解會交盾俾SAM</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係針佢左膠定黑人問題<br />\n而係佢個角色定位去到現實演員，點睇都冇領袖氣質<br />\n講立場佢一直都只係CA跟尾應聲蟲，講實力又輸過比Antman<br />\n谷佢上位把撚咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更唔好講同為打過WW2既英雄Bucky都同場<br />\n點睇最後交代吹水都應該由Bucky去，火花同感觸位實大過柒頭Falcon  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知呢幕Russo bros實有私心<br />\n因為佢地講過好鍾意Falcon個角色想拍佢個人電影<br />\n<br />\n但作為Fans，真心認為係食撚左屎先有呢個決定去拍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:15:12.000Z","msg":"樓主作為fans<br />\n用一大篇廢話去否定原作既設定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2bb3750948a812724e1d2af9a0b572bed025f3","tid":1123261,"uid":89155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"補充返少少 我唔肯定有冇記錯<br />\n漫畫入面steve rogers係打iron nails嗰陣冇左超級戰士血清 最後差啲死添<br />\n係falcon救返佢條命 之後rogers先比falcon做美國隊長。<br />\n所以我都係認為係電影舖排有問題<br />\n本身falcon做captain america爭議唔算好大"},{"pid":"104618e754cd3af7dc4d34364759940272ba5c29","tid":1123261,"uid":66822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"marvel 電影正式收皮<br />\n 以後嘅作品只會越來越差"},{"pid":"2e5cf71e70090233690e071a9cbd1fc14a685c94","tid":1123261,"uid":179588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"610fcd87cb150862cfabbfea2b1b7c37250c720f","tid":1123261,"uid":26106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5bd0556b01f09ccb83909445d586ae3eea9c6ec3","tid":1123261,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點撚解會交盾俾SAM</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係針佢左膠定黑人問題<br />\n而係佢個角色定位去到現實演員，點睇都冇領袖氣質<br />\n講立場佢一直都只係CA跟尾應聲蟲，講實力又輸過比Antman<br />\n谷佢上位把撚咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更唔好講同為打過WW2既英雄Bucky都同場<br />\n點睇最後交代吹水都應該由Bucky去，火花同感觸位實大過柒頭Falcon  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知呢幕Russo bros實有私心<br />\n因為佢地講過好鍾意Falcon個角色想拍佢個人電影<br />\n<br />\n但作為Fans，真心認為係食撚左屎先有呢個決定去拍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:15:12.000Z","msg":"樓主作為fans<br />\n用一大篇廢話去否定原作既設定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"原作係bucky都有做過cap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a8b7161ab4c59c5ee7d5b8bfed570413f2ae61","tid":1123261,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e5cf71e70090233690e071a9cbd1fc14a685c94","tid":1123261,"uid":179588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"610fcd87cb150862cfabbfea2b1b7c37250c720f","tid":1123261,"uid":26106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5bd0556b01f09ccb83909445d586ae3eea9c6ec3","tid":1123261,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點撚解會交盾俾SAM</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係針佢左膠定黑人問題<br />\n而係佢個角色定位去到現實演員，點睇都冇領袖氣質<br />\n講立場佢一直都只係CA跟尾應聲蟲，講實力又輸過比Antman<br />\n谷佢上位把撚咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更唔好講同為打過WW2既英雄Bucky都同場<br />\n點睇最後交代吹水都應該由Bucky去，火花同感觸位實大過柒頭Falcon  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知呢幕Russo bros實有私心<br />\n因為佢地講過好鍾意Falcon個角色想拍佢個人電影<br />\n<br />\n但作為Fans，真心認為係食撚左屎先有呢個決定去拍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:15:12.000Z","msg":"樓主作為fans<br />\n用一大篇廢話去否定原作既設定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"原作係bucky都有做過cap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n咁又點？<br />\n依家講緊樓豬一開始一大段野已經否定sam<br />\n話佢冇資格又乘<br />\n唔識閱讀理解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}